    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a solid choice for someone looking for a functional daily driver at a reasonable price. The exterior shows its age with some noticeable paint fading on the upper surfaces and a few minor dings and scratches around the body. Inside, the cabin is intact but displays typical wear and tear on the upholstery and high-touch areas. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though it may require some routine maintenance or minor repairs in the near future to keep it at its best. It's a dependable car that has been used regularly and is priced to reflect its current state.",
