      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s been such a reliable companion. It's in really solid shape\u2014runs smoothly and has been well-loved! I\u2019ve made sure to keep up with everything so it's ready for its next adventure with you. It\u2019s a great find for anyone wanting a dependable car that still looks and feels fantastic. Feel free to reach out if you want to come see it!",
      "price": 28500.0,
